"</shortcut> <guimenu>खेल</guimenu> <guimenuitem>निर्गम</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:308
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Exit</action> &i18n-knavalbattle;."
msgstr "<action>निर्गम</action> &i18n-knavalbattle;।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Change Nickname…</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>उपनाम परिवर्तयतु…</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: action
#: index.docbook:323
#, no-c-format
msgid "Change the default nickname."
msgstr "पूर्वनिर्धारितं उपनाम परिवर्तयन्तु ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Play Sounds</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>ध्वनयः वादयन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle whether sounds (played when shooting) should be played.</"
"action> The default is on."
msgstr ""
"<action>ध्वनयः (शूटिंग् करणसमये वाद्यन्ते) वादयितव्याः वा इति टॉग्ल् कुर्वन्तु ।</action> "
"पूर्वनिर्धारितं चालू अस्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Adjacent Ships</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>समीपस्थानि जहाजानि</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Toggle whether the ships can be put on a desk without one empty "
"space between them.</action> The default is on. This setting should be "
"defined on a host when <link linkend=\"howtoplay\">playing &i18n-"
"knavalbattle; via network</link>."
msgstr ""
"<action>जहाजाः तयोः मध्ये एकं रिक्तस्थानं विना मेजस्य उपरि स्थापयितुं शक्यन्ते वा इति टोग्ल् "
"कुर्वन्तु ।</action> पूर्वनिर्धारितं चालू अस्ति । एतत् सेटिङ्ग् एकस्मिन् होस्ट् इत्यत्र परिभाषितं "
"भवेत् यदा<link linkend=\"howtoplay\"> क्रीडन् &amp;i18n-knavalbattle; जालद्वारा</"
"link> ."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show End-of-Game Message</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>क्रीडासमाप्तसन्देशं दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you won the game and have a new highscore, the highscore dialog will be "
"shown. Otherwise the result is displayed in the statusbar or, if this option "
"is enabled, additionally in a dialog."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् क्रीडां जित्वा नूतनः उच्चाङ्कः अस्ति तर्हि उच्चाङ्कसंवादः दर्शितः भविष्यति । "
"अन्यथा परिणामः स्थितिपट्टिकायां अथवा, यदि एषः विकल्पः सक्षमः अस्ति, तर्हि अतिरिक्तरूपेण "
"संवादे प्रदर्शितः भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:374
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Left Grid</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Right Grid</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>वामजालं दर्शयतु</guimenuitem> "
"<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guimenuitem>दक्षिणजालं दर्शयतु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the grids makes it easier to place a shot with the mouse pointer."
msgstr "जालपुटानां उपयोगेन मूषकसूचकेन सह शॉट् स्थापयितुं सुकरं भवति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:389
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Difficulty</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> <guisubmenu>कठिनता</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:395
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game difficulty setting (<guimenuitem>Easy</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Medium</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Hard</guimenuitem>) has "
"effect only in single player games against the computer. In higher levels "
"the AI uses a smarter strategy for shooting and placing ships."
msgstr ""
"क्रीडाकठिनतासेटिंग् (<guimenuitem>सुलभ</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>मध्यम</"
"guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>कठिन</guimenuitem>) केवलं सङ्गणकविरुद्धेषु एकक्रीडकक्रीडासु "
"एव प्रभावं करोति उच्चस्तरस्य एआइ जहाजानां शूटिंग्, स्थापनार्थं च चतुरतरं रणनीतिं प्रयुङ्क्ते ।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally &i18n-knavalbattle; has the common &kde; <guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu> and <guimenu>Help</guimenu> menu items, for more information read "
"the sections about the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus.html#menus-"
"settings\">Settings Menu</ulink> and <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/menus."
"html#menus-help\">Help Menu</ulink> of the &kde; Fundamentals."
msgstr ""
"अतिरिक्तरूपेण &i18n-knavalbattle; सामान्यं &kde; <guimenu>सेटिंग्स्</guimenu> तथा "
"<guimenu>सहायता</guimenu> मेनू-वस्तूनाम्, अधिकसूचनार्थं <ulink url=\"help:/"
"fundamentals/menus.html#menus-settings\">सेटिंग्स् मेन्यू< इत्यस्य विषये विभागान् पठन्तु /"
"ulink> तथा च &kde; मौलिकता।"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:414
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "बहुधा पृष्टाः प्रश्नाः"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid "I'm not sure where to shoot, can I get a hint?"
msgstr "अहं न निश्चितः यत् कुत्र शूटिंग् कर्तव्यम्, किं अहं संकेतं प्राप्नुयाम्?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:425
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, there is no hint system in &i18n-knavalbattle;."
msgstr "न, &i18n-knavalbattle; इत्यत्र संकेतव्यवस्था नास्ति।"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:433
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I rotate a ship?"
msgstr "कथं पोतं परिभ्रमितुं शक्नोमि ?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:438
#, no-c-format
msgid "Move the ship where you want to place it, then press the &RMB;."
msgstr "यत्र भवन्तः तत् स्थापयितुम् इच्छन्ति तत्र जहाजं चालयन्तु, ततः &RMB;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:446
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change how the game looks?"
msgstr "क्रीडा कथं दृश्यते इति परिवर्तयितुं शक्नोमि वा?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:451
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, the theme is not changeable."
msgstr "न, विषयः परिवर्तनशीलः नास्ति।"

